@no_majority_prussia
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: weimar_coalition_prussia <= 50 and grand_coalition_prussia <= 50 and bourgeois_coalition_prussia <= 50 and center_right_coalition_prussia <= 50 and right_coalition_prussia <= 50 and nlp_pl <= 50
on-arrival: nlp_prussia = 1 if was_nlp_prussia; in_nlp_majority_prussia = 1 if was_in_nlp_majority_prussia; in_weimar_coalition_prussia = 1 if was_in_weimar_coalition_prussia; in_grand_coalition_prussia = 1 if was_in_grand_coalition_prussia; in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia = 1 if was_in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia; in_center_right_coalition_prussia = 1 if was_in_center_right_coalition_prussia; in_right_coalition_prussia = 1 if was_in_right_coalition_prussia;

There is no path to a majority government for now. The current government will stay in power as a minority coalition.





