@fischbeck_nlp
title: Otto Fischbeck (<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>, Constitutional Liberal).
view-if: nlp_prussia and vldp_formed
choose-if: in_nlp_majority_prussia or (in_grand_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl + z_pl > spd_pl) or (in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl > z_pl) or (in_center_right_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl > z_pl)
unavailable-subtitle: Fischbeck doesn't have needed support to become the Minister-President.
on-arrival: prussia_leader = "Fischbeck"; prussia_leader_party = nlp_name;
face-image: img/portraits/FischbeckOtto.jpg

WIP.

@kardorff
title: Siegfried Kardorff (<span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>, Left-Wing Stresemannite).
view-if: nlp_prussia
choose-if: in_nlp_majority_prussia or (in_grand_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl + z_pl > spd_pl) or (in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl > z_pl) or (in_center_right_coalition_prussia and nlp_pl > z_pl) or (in_right_coalition_prussia and ((nlp_pl > kswr_pl and kswr_exist) or (nlp_pl > dnvp_pl and dnvp_ideology = "Radical")))
unavailable-subtitle: Kardorff doesn't have needed support to become the Minister-President.
on-arrival: prussia_leader = "Kardorff"; prussia_leader_party = nlp_name;
face-image: img/portraits/KardorffSiegfried.jpg

WIP.

