@stegerwald
title: Adam Stegerwald (<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span>)
view-if: in_weimar_coalition_prussia or in_grand_coalition_prussia or in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia or in_center_right_coalition_prussia or in_right_coalition_prussia
choose-if: (in_weimar_coalition_prussia and z_pl > spd_pl) or (in_grand_coalition_prussia and (nlp_pl + z_pl) > spd_pl) or in_bourgeois_coalition_prussia or in_center_right_coalition_prussia or in_right_coalition_prussia
unavailable-subtitle: Stegerwald doesn't have needed support to become the Minister-President.
on-arrival: prussia_leader = "Stegerwald"; prussia_leader_party = "Z";
face-image: img/portraits/StegerwaldAdam.jpg

