@schiele
title: Martin Schiele ([?if not dnvp_ideology = "Radical":<span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>?][?if kvp_exist:<span style="color: #455B95;">**KVP**</span>?]).
view-if: in_center_right_coalition_prussia or in_right_coalition_prussia
choose-if: (in_center_right_coalition_prussia and (nlp_pl + dnvp_pl + rlb_pl) > (z_pl + fvp_pl)) or in_right_coalition_prussia
unavailable-subtitle: Schiele doesn't have needed support to become the Minister-President.
on-arrival: prussia_leader = "Schiele"; prussia_leader_party = "DNVP" if not dnvp_ideology = "Radical"; prussia_leader_party = "KVP" if kvp_exist;
face-image: img/portraits/SchieleMartin.jpg

WIP.

@gayl
title: Wilhelm Gayl ([?if dnvp_ideology = "Radical":<span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>?][?if kswr_exist:<span style="color: #003755;">**KSWR**</span>?])
view-if: in_right_coalition_prussia and (kswr_exist or dnvp_ideology = "Radical")
choose-if: (in_right_coalition_prussia and ((kswr_pl > z_pl and kswr_exist) or (dnvp_pl > z_pl and dnvp_ideology = "Radical")))
unavailable-subtitle: Gayl doesn't have needed support to become the Minister-President.
on-arrival: prussia_leader = "Gayl"; prussia_leader_party = "DNVP" if dnvp_ideology = "Radical"; prussia_leader_party = "KSWR" if kswr_exist;
face-image: img/portraits/GaylWilhelm.jpg

WIP.
